ҰThis is not the end; it is not even the beginning of the end
but perhaps, the end of the beginning 
For my mum - my best friend and role model
Anita Shaw 1948 2008"Ә
§IN LOVING MEMORY OF
MUM, LILLIAN GRACE PINFOLD (NEE BOREHAM)
BORN INWORTH STREET, BATTERSEA ON JUNE 4TH 1914
PASSED AWAY OCTOBER 7TH 2008
AND GREATLY MISSED BY ALL"Ә
§In fond memory of
Our Founder Mrs June Mackay
Our Chairman John Perry
and Secretary Mrs Louise Perry (nee Conner)
from the members of the Brixton Dog Training Club"«
ЁIn Loving Memory of Barbara Alice Harper
1934 2015
She was passionate about her gardening and enjoyed sharing
her love of nature and wildlife with family and friends"¬
©MICHAEL HORSMAN 1932-2009
Architect of Ralph West Hall, Albert Bridge Road
Built 1962, demolished 2000
No hell below, no heaven above
Live life now and act with love"®
